# Runtime SQLite database (trajectories, steps, screenshots BLOB, digests, traces,
# eval_cases, failure_memory). Rebuilt by "Import Dataset" from the frontend
# or POST /api/import/molmoweb-sample. WAL/shm sidecars are also ignored.
data/trajecta.db
data/trajecta.db-wal
data/trajecta.db-shm

# ChromaDB persistent store
data/chroma/

# Evaluation data root: a snapshot of data/ used as the isolated baseline for
# `python -m backend.app.agent_eval`. Same shape as data/ (trajecta.db, chroma,
# eval_cases mirror), but disposable — rebuild with `cp -r data eval/data` when
# the baseline needs to be refreshed.
eval/data/

# Eval artifacts. Per S18 "experiment results, reproducible", the committed
# evidence is: eval/golden.jsonl, eval/ragas_report.{json,md}, the latest
# eval/agent_report.{json,md}, docs/experiment_log.md, and ONE canonical run
# under eval/runs/ (agent_report + traces + the final judge/ with the κ report)
# so the judge/RAGAS results are re-runnable offline. Other (debug/iteration)
# runs under eval/runs/ and the mock smoke test stay local-only.
eval/_mock_smoke_test.json
eval/runs/*
!eval/runs/2026-06-03T05-45-39Z/
eval/runs/2026-06-03T05-45-39Z/judge_v1/
eval/runs/2026-06-03T05-45-39Z/judge_v2_run1/

.vite
dist/
node_modules/

